onApply(Reward, Leveler, int) - Methode in Schnittstelle net.jandie1505.playerlevels.core.rewards.RewardExecutor
This method is called when the reward is applied to the player.
This method should do the things the reward does when it gets applied.
If the upgrade has successfully been applied, this method has to return true.

PlayerPointsReward - Klasse in net.jandie1505.playerlevels.core.rewards.types
This is a reward that give a player a specific amount of points when applied.
You can get the data using PlayerPointsReward.createMilestone(String, String, int) or PlayerPointsReward.createInterval(String, String, int, int, int).
The reward uses a formula which has the variables level and xp.
